{
  "text": "To solve the above problem, inspired by the Squeezeand-Excitation (SE) block [CITATION_1] , we further append several Convolutional Attention Modules (CAM) in the modified MobileNetV2 to select the informative channels. Thus, we take advantage of the weights generated by CAM to guide the network learning and thus the weighted feature maps can be obtained. Such an approach is beneficial for emphasizing the important information and suppressing the irrelevant information.",
